      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented build and release process; unit tests covering core numerical routines pass at release.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM-based fork v3.1.2) is maintained under Git version control with tagged releases. A CI pipeline executes 142 unit tests on each commit; all pass at the v3.1.2 release tag. Release notes document one mesh-import crash fixed in v3.0.9; the production v3.1.2 build was used for all COU1 analyses. Software quality assurance is assessed at Gradation 2, meeting the MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
