      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification for primary transport equations using manufactured solutions or benchmark cases.",
      "rationale": "Spatial order of accuracy for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver was verified against the 3-D lid-driven cavity benchmark (Re=1000) and the Taylor-Green vortex manufactured solution. Observed order of accuracy of 1.87 (target ≥ 1.5 for second-order schemes) was confirmed. All verification runs completed nominally with converged residuals and no floating-point exceptions reported."
    },
    {
