      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry using the same blood analog and the same 5 flow-speed combinations defined in the COU. The geometric tolerance variations in the sensitivity sweep bracket the manufacturing tolerances specified in the device design history file. Validation activities are assessed as directly relevant to the COU at Gradation 2."
    },
