      "rationale": "All 27 sensitivity sweep cases and 4 validation cases achieved residuals ≤ 1e-5 for continuity, momentum, and turbulence transport equations. Pressure-velocity coupling used SIMPLE with under-relaxation factors of 0.3/0.7. No divergence or solver stall was observed in any production run. Numerical solver error assessed at Gradation 1, meeting the MRL 2 minimum requirement."
