      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on published benchmark studies for centrifugal blood pump flows (Fraser et al. 2011, Hariharan et al. 2011). The power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen et al.) is the FDA-recommended formulation. Model form uncertainty is acknowledged and considered acceptable at MRL 2. Assessed at Gradation 1."
