    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 requirements matrix. Validation results demonstrate NIH prediction within 15% of experimental measurements across all 5 operating points, and the relative hemolysis index RH = 0.87 satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion at the worst-case geometric combination. The software quality assurance factor confirms the production solver version is release-qualified. All simulation runs completed nominally with converged residuals. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for this Class II CPB device at MRL 2.",
